setPrereqs("Satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements, and courses 1, 2, and 3. Enrollment restricted to senior anthropology majors. Enrollment by permission of instructor")
setPrereqs("Satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements, and courses 1, 2, and 3")
