setInstruct("D. Rutherford")
setCourse("267A")
setTitle("Science and Justice: Experiments in Collaboration")
setTerms("S")
setDescrip("Considers the practical and epistemological necessity of collaborative research in the development of new sciences and technologies that are attentive to questions of ethics and justice. Enrollment by permission of instructor. Enrollment restricted to graduate students. (Also offered as Feminist Studies 268A. Students cannot receive credit for both courses).")
