setTitle("The Image of Arhat in China")
setTerms("*")
setDescrip("Indian Buddhist sage-monks (arhats) are portrayed in China in ways that represent a remarkable variety of visual/historical/practice traditions. This seminar examines these depictions and explores the ranges of means and functions attached to this theme.")
setEnrollRestrict("graduate students")
